title: Skype usage reach in the United States 2018 , by age group
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Reach. In total the number of data points it has is 7.
Overall Reach has decreased over the Year.
Reach is roughly constant from 18-24 to 25-34, gradually decreasing from 25-34 to 55-64, roughly constant from 55-64 to 65-75, and finally slightly decreasing from 65-75 to 75+.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 25-34 and 35-44.
Maximum Reach, about 52.0 was reported at Year 25-34
Minimum Reach about 16.0 was reached at Year 75+
